<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880526-0178 </DOCNO><HL> Harris to Combine Eight Units </HL><SO> </SO><CO> HRS WNEWS </CO><DATELINE> MELBOURNE, Fla.  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Harris Corp. said that, as part of a restructuring, it is combining its eight informations-system divisions into a new unit.    The communications concern said the eight divisions had fiscal 1987 sales of approximately $640 million.    Harris said the new single unit, which retains the name Information Systems Sector, will be headed by James R. Oyler, Harris's senior vice president. </TEXT></DOC>